title: Wimbledon 2009 - Womens Final - Day 12 (4th July 2009)
description:
Wimbledon 2009 - Womens Final - Day 12 (4th July 2009)

Saturday 4th July 2009
1:30pm - 6:10pm
BBC1



Sue Barker presents live coverage from SW19, where a repeat of last year's final sees the Williams sisters facing each other once more on Centre Court. The rangy grass-court expert, Venus, against the more muscular, aggressive Serena, who is aiming - if not for revenge (they are sisters, after all) - then at least to avoid finding herself in her taller sibling's shadow for the second year running.
